  "content": "ot/corvia-project/corvia-workspace/repos/corvia-adapter-git && cargo test module_resolver`\nExpected: All 5 tests pass.\n\n**Step 5: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add -A && git commit -m \"feat(m3.4): add RustModuleMap for cross-file import resolution (D72)\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Integrate `RustModuleMap` into AstChunker and treesitter\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `corvia-adapter-git/src/ast_chunker.rs`\n- Modify: `corvia-adapter-git/src/treesitter.rs` (lines 165-171, 200-243, 414-422)\n- Modify: `corvia-adapter-git/src/git.rs` (lines 38-45)\n\n**Step 1: Update `AstChunker` to hold an optional module map**\n\nIn `corvia-adapter-git/src/ast_chunker.rs`, change the struct and impl:\n\n```rust\nuse crate::module_resolver::RustModuleMap;\nuse std::sync::Arc;\n\npub struct AstChunker {\n    module_map: Option<Arc<RustModuleMap>>,\n}\n\nimpl AstChunker {\n    pub fn new() -> Self {\n        Self { module_map: None }\n    }\n\n    pub fn with_module_map(module_map: Arc<RustModuleMap>) -> Self {\n        Self {\n            module_map: Some(module_map),\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\nUpdate the `chunk()` method to pass the module map through:\n\n```rust\nfn chunk(&self, source: &str, meta: &SourceMetadata) -> Result<ChunkResult> {\n    let result = treesitter::chunk_file_with_relations(\n        &meta.file_path,\n        source,\n        &meta.extension,\n        self.module_map.as_deref(),\n    );\n    // ... rest unchanged\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Update treesitter entry points to accept `Option<&RustModuleMap>`**\n\nIn `corvia-adapter-git/src/treesitter.rs`:\n\nChange `chunk_file_with_relations` signature (line 167):\n```rust\npub fn chunk_file_with_relations(\n    file_path: &str,\n    source: &str,\n    extension: &str,\n    module_map: Option<&RustModuleMap>,",
